# Built web app bundle (shipped via package.json "files", served by the plugin) — build output, not
# source. Anchored to the repo root so it does NOT swallow webapp/public/ (the Vite static-source dir
# holding the PWA manifest, icon, and service worker, which ARE tracked).
/public/
